title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 29 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 29 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3: Clay and Buck recap their newsmaking conversation with President Trump. Clay and Buck play highlights from their interview with Trump. Media not curious about Biden's mental health, spent 4 years questioning Trump's mental health. Trump says he'll decide on 2024 after the 2020 midterms. Clay and Buck preview tomorrow's show.
